channel.title: Discovery Shuttle Launch
channel.description: Hello everyone, I want to hear everyones thoughts on the shuttle launch that happened today. It was shuttle Discovery's 39th and last launch. I personally did not get to watch it, I just watched a video on youtube. My science teacher was all excited about this so I wanna know if anyone of you guys are. Tell me what you thought, did you like it, did you watch it, did you think it was boring, Post your thoughts!
